<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Min khat ka ngaih nawp chuh a um,
 La a sak ka nuom hi;
 Zie min chun ei sukipak hi,
 Lei chunga min hawihpen.

[V2]
 Aw, Isu, ka hehpih (3)
 Ei hehpih masak ziek.

[V3]
 2. Hukdampa hehpihna ei hilh,
 Suohchak na'ng a thi chu;
 A thisan lul chuh ei hetsak,
 Migilo thienna chuh.

[V4]
 3. Nicheng in ei hetsak zing hi,
 Ka Pa hehpihna chuh;
 Lampi thimah chieh mahleng le,
 Ka lampi A salhvak.

[V5]
 4. A hehpih lunggil ei hetsak,
 Dahna pen ei nem chuh;
 Ka lungkhamna ei thawkpih hi,
 Mi dang hih theihloh chuh.</lyrics>
<title>THERE IS A NAME I LOVE TO HEAR</title>
</song>